SUMMARY:MEDIOCRACY – TERRA TOMA // (WM Im Gastgarten) (Uhrzeit prüfen)
LOCATION:Cafe Carina
DESCRIPTION:MEDIOCRACY – TERRA TOMA // (WM im Gastgarten)  MEDIOCRACY is a newly formed band from Vienna\, Austria.  MEDIOCRACY veers along the edges of a multitude of genres it draws influence from\, combining a signature mixture of harsh sounds\, complex melodic arrangements and unexpected\, unique elements that will restore your faith in not having already heard everything that is out there.  Our mission is to bring you music that holds both raw heartfelt emotion as well as sophisticated songwriting that will captivate beyond just the first listen.  https://www.instagram.com/mediocracy_at/  Chris — Guitar\, Co-Composer FlowG — Guitar\, Composer\, Background Vocals Fuchsi — Drums Xander — Lead Vocals\, Keyboard  TERRA TOMA released their new album „Savoir Vivre“ in 2025 and will deliver some unreleased material that is going to be released next year! https://www.facebook.com/terratoma
